<BODY>
<SLUG> BC-R-ELECTRIC-CARS-REVIEW-NYT </SLUG>
<HEADLINE>
TAKE THIS CAR AND PLUG IT 
</HEADLINE>
  
(Repeating for all needing.) (The Week in Review) 
(bl) 
 By MATTHEW L. WALD   
 c.1998 N.Y. Times News Service    
<TEXT>
<P>
   WASHINGTON _ Once upon a time, 1998 was going to be the year of
the electric car. In 1990 California announced that 2 percent of
