   AUTHOR-PATRICK-DILLON (Seattle) Interview with Patrick Dillon,
author of ``Lost at Sea,'' a book on the 1983 sinking of two crab
boats from Anacortes in the Bering Sea in which 14 persons lost
their lives. PHOTO.
</P>
