expected to determine the future of separatism in the province.
Polls close 8 p.m. Eastern time. By Anthony DePalma.
</P>
<P>
   CHINA-ECON (Beijing) _ Countering reports that its economic
reform plan has foundered, China strongly reiterates its intention
to overhaul the country's debt-ridden system of state-owned
industries. By Elisabeth Rosenthal
</P>
