prevention of cancer, including breast cancer. The American Cancer
Society estimates that diet is a primary factor in a third of
cancer deaths. But pop science that holds that fish oils, for
example, ``prevent'' cancer just doesn't hold up under scrutiny. By
Jane E. Brody. (1150 words)
