<P>
   CLINTON-BAPTISTS &QL;
</P>
<P>
   UNDATED _ Do President Clinton's sexual sins have a connection
with his Baptist upbringing? Newsweek religion correspondent
Kenneth L. Woodward posed that question Nov. 2 in an essay, ``Sex,
Sin and Salvation,'' that brought a flood of responses. By JIM
JONES. Story will move in ``l'' lifestyle category. &QL; 
 &QL; 
 &QL;
</P>
<P>
   E N T E R T A I N M E N T &QL; 
 &QL; 
 &QL;
</P>
<P>
   CHRISTMAS-CDS &QL;
</P>
<P>
   UNDATED _ Is it just us, or are there more Christmas CDs out
this year than ever before? The only thing missing is ``A Metallica
Christmas _ Thrashin' the Favorites,'' but there's a good chance
that's coming in the mail today. Until then, here's a look at the
top holiday CD offerings. By Fort Worth Star-Telegram critics.
Story will move in ``e'' entertainment category. &QL; 
