</HEADER>
<BODY>
<SLUG> BC-SPOT-BJT-COX </SLUG>
<HEADLINE>
&HT;   
</HEADLINE>
 1201 UPDATE &HT;    UPDATE
 &HT;    The Cox News Service spot news budget for Tuesday, Dec. 1, 1998.
 &HT;    c.1998 Cox News Service
<TEXT>
<P>
