just did it better. Credit the switch to Jon Kitna, who provided
the spark coach Dennis Erickson was looking for and also prompted
his teammates to play better than they have. Now comes a much
tougher test, when they face the New York Jets' fourth-rated
defense Sunday in the Meadowlands.
