holiday shopping season is over. According to analysts, the season
got off to a rousing start Friday as millions of apparently
confident consumers awoke at the crack of dawn to hit the
southland's malls and department stores. Did the trend continue
through the weekend? What does this portent for the season as a
whole? By Enrique Rivero. (Will move in the ``f'' financial news
